{"tid":1984103,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"有生意頭腦　明日花綺羅向買衫粉絲貼心送罩","createTime":"2020-04-22T08:48:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-23T10:48:27.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"00b23d9bd219762ea48867a3ebd4f6d5907ed90d","tid":1984103,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T08:48:35.000Z","msg":"31歲前日本AV天后明日花綺羅，今年初正式宣布退出AV。她從良後積極進軍商界，開設美容院又創立自家內衣服裝品牌，深受當地女性歡迎。<br />\n<br />\n甚有生意頭腦的明日花，眼見近日當地疫情嚴重，向網購其服裝的粉絲附上自己的靚postcard外，更驚喜送上口罩，包裝上面更貼心寫上慰問說話，祝願大家身體健康。有女粉絲直言：「比收到安倍晉三的布口罩開心100倍！」，大讚她是真女神。"},{"pid":"1840efcfa56da0315dee9a80f164fa17f7f6d660","tid":1984103,"uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T08:48:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200422/photo/bkn-20200422162016361-0422_00862_001_03p.jpg?20200422162947\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20200422%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200422162016361-0422_00862_001_03p.jpg%3F20200422162947&h=8e7adf69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200422/photo/bkn-20200422162016361-0422_00862_001_04p.jpg?20200422162947\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20200422%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200422162016361-0422_00862_001_04p.jpg%3F20200422162947&h=bf62e81e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d903a97e1455c611cae4c66a5507a4850832d668","tid":1984103,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T08:49:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200422/photo/bkn-20200422162016361-0422_00862_001_05p.jpg?20200422162947\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20200422%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200422162016361-0422_00862_001_05p.jpg%3F20200422162947&h=3e478d39&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有網民話比收到安倍晉三的布口罩開心100倍！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http